Author notes
Map by Elistas - This map is my first source map. -=)[H2o](=- is the name of my team. The building in the map comes from this name. A 'H' with four towers and a double door, a '2' which is a long bunker, and a 'O', a great battle place with many glasses waiting to be broken. There are two buyzone, on the H and in the O. Enjoy ! ;)
